fulltitle: Mulgrew Miller: Advice for Young Jazz Musicians
description:
Please help support my work as the Jazz Video Guy:  https://www.patreon.com/bretprimack

Pianist Mulgrew Miller has some advice for young Jazz musicians who want to learn how to improvise and play with other musicians.
